title: Bio
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Fast food, Take-out, French, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small French organic creperie next door to Barney's store. Offers breakfast & lunch with the majority of dishes being gluten free. Order at counter and sit outside at a sidewalk table, or take your food to Union Square park. Has vegan soup, salad, and a few vegan baked goods in the pastry case. Offers fresh organic fruit juice purees.
